<b><u>Track Record:</b></u><br>
This variant was only used in one tournament, where it went 2-0. However, it was an absolute machine in playtesting, and wiped the floor with just about everything in the pre-Reflections 2 environment. The release of WYS forced me to adapt and drop the dueling aspect. Thus, Chain Of Command was born.<br>
